text: Knema globularia is a species of plant in the family Myristicaceae. It is a tree found in Cambodia, China, India, Indonesia, Laos, Malaysia, Myanmar, Singapore, Thailand, and Vietnam. ==References== Category:Flora of Indo-China globularia Category:Trees of China Category:Flora of Assam (region) Category:Trees of Indo-China Category:Trees of Malaya Category:Trees of Sumatra Category:Least concern plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
